headline: Omnicom Group (OMC) Stock Is Up, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of global advertising giant Omnicom Group (NYSE:OMC) jumped 4.5% in the afternoon session after the company announced a 14% increase in its quarterly dividend and Citi reaffirmed its "Buy" rating on the stock.
